data.description:
Location! Pride of ownership is shown in this gorgeous residence. Perfect location, better than a new build & upgrades galore! Discover a delightful interior showcasing fresh soothing palette, tile flooring, a formal dining. The remarkable kitchen boasts white shaker cabinets, stylish tile backsplash, a walk-in pantry, quartz counters, dazzling light fixtures, & an island equipped with a breakfast bar ideal for those quick morning coffees. You will find a versatile loft perfect for entertaining! Doors open to the main retreat comprised of soft carpet, a private bathroom with dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Host memorable gatherings in the wonderful backyard featuring an extended covered patio, a sparkling new heated swimming pool. This beauty won't disappoint! Schedule your showing today The upgrades include top of the line extended kitchen cabinets, Bedrosian Cloe backsplash tile, accent walls, sun protecting screens, top of the line fans & lighting, you will enjoy the owned soft water system and the Solar panels. Heated pool to enjoy year round was recently built in, along with the fabulous decorative pavers & the upgraded synthetic grass. And so much more...
The state of the art alarm & cameras can stay. Close to all the major highways, near shopping and many restaurants. Don't miss this great opportunity.
